    <note type="biography">
        <p>German-born governess. Daughter of Richard Ludwig, accountant, of Hamburg. Governess to the Darwin family, 1860–3. Translated German works for CD. Married Reginald Saint Pattrick, vicar of Sellinge, Kent (<hi rend="italic">Alum. Oxon.</hi>), in 1874.</p></note>
